{"tid":1824453,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"原來我是混血兒！ - 高慧然","createTime":"2020-01-14T12:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-14T16:05:31.000Z","uid":25558,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"c345c849ceb70dfc3dee4ec2a074f35963cb3320","tid":1824453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:38:09.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200114/20842924/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200114%2F20842924%2F&d=RrW1hT%2ByM3GEQeJ1bMSerrZiocJRpRWN%2FMrNqpcM%2BY8%3D&h=b1730395\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.lifestyle.appledaily.com%2Flifestyle%2Fcolumnist%2F%25E9%25AB%2598%25E6%2585%25A7%25E7%2584%25B6%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20200114%2F20842924%2F&h=da703fd5\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/columnist/%E9%AB%98%E6%85%A7%E7%84%B6/daily/article/20200114/20842924/</a><br />\n<br />\n原來我是混血兒！ - 高慧然<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple_sub/20200114/large/1578898547_0ce9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple_sub%2F20200114%2Flarge%2F1578898547_0ce9.jpg&h=586174f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n689退休之後，可能缺乏家庭溫暖，被老婆仔女忽略，又不好意思去屯門看大媽表演，所以攬住部電腦，或者手機取暖，日日在網上發表獨特見解，日子有功，變成了KOL。我很替他高興，要知道，很多人退休之後太失落，不是精神出現問題，便是突然患上絕症。而且大腦不用的話，很容易變老年癡呆。所以，即使689發表一些怪論，被很多網民批評沒有邏輯上的合理性，我也傾向於給他正面鼓勵。比如他質疑港島區只住了百零萬人，不大可能容納百幾萬示威者，我就覺得他凡事質疑的態度是對的，正如他老婆只有他一個老公，卻生了三個仔女，我用他的邏輯想了半天，沒想出答案。沒關係，這個問題交給689去思考吧，我的思緒被他的新發現牽動了。<br />\n<br />\n689的新發現是，香港的年輕人都是中國製造的，因為他們日日飲東江水，所以身體絕大多數水份來自東江水。<br />\n<br />\n恭喜689！這個一定是醫學上最重大的發現，退休廢老689唔單止成為網紅，更有望獲得諾貝爾醫學獎，為香港人爭光！原來從醫學上解構，一個人飲甚麼水，可以決定他的基因。問題是，我比689更貼地，更了解香港年輕人，我知道很多人是飲可樂大的，也許，香港九成年輕人其實是美國人？<br />\n<br />\n至於我自己，我九成飲品其實是法國紅酒，幾年前迷上智利酒，最近轉飲澳洲白酒，口渴時則以法國1664解渴，天寒地凍時鍾情蘇格蘭威士忌，我現在才知道我是混血兒！ <br />\n<br />\n高慧然<br />\n電郵 :kowaiyin2004@yahoo.com.hk"},{"pid":"704d8ccc0a31c59023d51d593b87991c1fd7be72","tid":1824453,"uid":229920,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:40:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864dc3d10832eb310ccc24009df59c37a19c8267","tid":1824453,"uid":91432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:40:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">【緊急】</span>好多<span style=\"color: red;\">白人左翼</span>抹黑<span style=\"color: blue;\">香港人</span>！！！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1824339/page/1\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1824339/page/1</a></strong></strong></span>"},{"pid":"1173f34ffd31fce18f75422f9a5621d6050b2e62","tid":1824453,"uid":37869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:41:17.000Z","msg":"食咩米就係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"71a7cdb1b49ff92bcbef83fef52f20cb9df2d35b","tid":1824453,"uid":55552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:43:12.000Z","msg":"笑撚死<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c6806b06d5751a279fc3ea9e569cb87194354412","tid":1824453,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-14T12:43:51.000Z","msg":"日期：2020年1月15日 星期三<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">中環:全民力拒 制度暴力 你我堅守 程序公義集會</span><br />\n時間 ： 1200-1400<br />\n地點 ：愛丁堡廣場<br />\n<span style=\"color: orange;\">(已獲發不反對通知書)</span><br /